Package nano.remexp.net

Interface Summary
EventSocketListener An interface that enables classes to act as event socket listeners and perform actions on events.
SocketReceiver An interface that enables classes to receive sockets from connectors.
StreamSocketInterface The interface for stream socket holders to allow them to be informed about a removed stream socket.
 

Class Summary
EventSocket This class holds the privilege of the socket and allows communication between all parts.
NanoComm The bits and pieces of the communication protocol.
NanoSocket The lowest layer of the communication between the different architectural parts.
NanoSocketObserver This class allows to observe running NanoSockets and check them for responses.
StreamSocket This class handles the stream sockets that receive stream data from the remote experiment.
